OL,5, The number of people contacting the    
OL,6, DVLA worried about a driver's ability  
OL,7, behind the wheel is rising, a Freedom  
OL,8, of Information request shows.          
OL,10,FExperts said older people should plan  
OL,11,Ftheir retirement from driving and      
OL,12,Frelatives should be having "difficult  
OL,13,Fconversations" with loved ones.        
OL,15,FIn 2022, 48,754 concerns over a        
OL,16,Fperson's fitness to drive were         
OL,17,Fsubmitted to the DVLA.                 
OL,19,FThe government said motorists must     
OL,20,Fensure they were fit to drive.         
